ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectOrder providing for assistance to New Brunswick potato producers
PrecisOrder authorizing Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into the AGREEMENT with New Brunswick to provide federal contributions of up to $15 million to assist potato producers in New Brunswick affected by excess rainfall in 2023 with the extraordinary costs incurred as a result of the extreme weather they experienced
